item.title: Meet Barbara Walters Only Daughter: Jacqueline Dena Guber, What Does She Do?
item.description: We assume that by this point you are all aware of the passing of legendary news woman Barbara Walters at the age of 93. She passed away on Friday, December 30, 2022, in the evening at her home in New York City, according to a report by ABC News. Among her loved ones, the pioneering TV journalist died away peacefully at home. The Today show’s first female co-host was Barbara Walters.
